### 🟡 MEDIUM — Missing Negative / Edge-Case Tests

The suite has **zero negative-path coverage**. These scenarios are likely production bug sources:

| Missing Test | Production Risk |
|---|---|
| `UpdatePrice` on non-existent SKU | Should throw `KeyNotFoundException` — never tested |
| `GetProduct` for missing SKU | Should return `null` — never tested |
| `Search` with no matches | Empty list behavior unverified |
| `ImportFromCsv` with malformed data | Will throw `IndexOutOfRangeException` or `FormatException` — no guard in prod code either |
| `ApplyBulkDiscount` with fraction > 1 or negative | Could produce negative prices — no validation |
| `RemoveProduct` on missing SKU | Silent no-op vs exception undefined |

Example fix for the most dangerous one:

